Hashtpar

Hashtpar (Persian: هشتپر‎, also known as, Gashpar, Hashtpar-e Tavalesh, Otak Saray, Otāq Sarai, Oţāq Sarāy, and Tālesh) is a city in and the capital of Talesh County, Gilan Province, Iran.

Lisar

Lisar (Persian: ليسار‎, also Romanized as Līsār and Lissar; also known as Līssār Bāzār) is a city in and the capital of Kargan Rud District, in Talesh County, Gilan Province, Iran.

Ava, Iran
